<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Order Confirmation</title>
    <style>
        /* Reset default styles */
        body, h1, p, ul, li {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }

        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: #fff;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }

        h1 {
            color: #333;
            font-size: 24px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        p {
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            line-height: 1.5;
            font-size: 16px;
        }

        ul {
            list-style: none;
            padding: 0;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        li {
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        li strong {
            font-weight: bold;
        }

        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 20px;
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #777;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h1>Order Confirmation</h1>
        <p>Thank you for your order!</p>
        <p>Here are the details of your order:</p>
        <ul>
            <li><strong>Order ID:</strong> <%= order._id %></li>
            <li><strong>Course Name:</strong> <%= order.name %></li>
            <li><strong>Price:</strong> <%= order.price %></li>
            <li><strong>Date:</strong> <%= order.date %></li>
        </ul>
        <p>If you have any questions or concerns about your order, please feel free to contact us.</p>
        <p>Thank you again for choosing our service!</p>
        <div class="footer">
            <p>&copy; 2024 Your Company Name. All rights reserved.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
